<HEADLINE>
<P>
COMMUNITY NEWS FOCUS: CITY GUIDE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 SEAL BEACH 
</P>
<P>
 Mayor: George Brown 
</P>
<P>
 Age: 70 
</P>
