through the Arroyo Simi Flood Control Channel that cuts through Moorpark, 
Ventura County Sheriff's Deputy Ernest Montagna said. 
</P>
<P>
 Soto was conscious but barely coherent when officers arrived at the scene, but 
later fell unconscious. 
