<TEXT>
<P>
 A 41-year-old man was shot seven times Friday in what police called a domestic 
dispute. 
</P>
<P>
 Luis Sanchez Chavez, of Santa Ana, was shot just after 5:30 p.m. in a driveway 
in the 1300 block of West Civic Center Drive, according to Santa Ana Police 
Sgt. Dick Faust. He was taken to UCI Medical Center, where he was in critical 
condition. 
</P>
