<P>
LOS ALAMITOS; HEZA FAST MAN WINS FEATURE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By STACY PIGOTT 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Trainer John Bassett only brought 10 horses to Los Alamitos this year, but if 
the other nine are anything like Heza Fast Man, California trainers had better 
watch out. 
</P>
<P>
 Heza Fast Man, who was making his Los Alamitos debut, won the $20,000 Vandy's 
Flash Handicap on Friday night under Henry Garcia by a neck. 
</P>
