a nonleague game Friday at Canyon High. 
</P>
<P>
 Hart (4-0) trailed in the first quarter, 14-7, before the Indians scored 49 
unanswered points.Palmdale (0-4) took its early lead on a pair of touchdown 
passes from quarterback Johnny Gillespie to Jamel White. 
