<HEADLINE>
<P>
CITY SECTION FOOTBALL ROUNDUP; IN ANOTHER VALLEY PAC-8 CONFERENCE OPENER: 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By KEVIN BOLT 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Reseda 36, Canoga Park 6 -- Michael Oxx rushed for 90 yards and scored two 
touchdowns, and defensive back Charles Shells returned an interception 25 yards 
and a punt 69 yards for touchdowns as the Regents dominated at Canoga Park. 
</P>
<P>
 Reseda (2-2, 1-0) limited Canoga Park (0-4, 0-1) to 105 yards and had seven 
sacks. Reseda forced five turnovers and turned three into scores. KEVIN BOLT 
</P>
