<HEADLINE>
<P>
SOUTHERN SECTION FOOTBALL ROUNDUP; CHANNEL LEAGUE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By DAVID HARRIS 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Dos Pueblos 24, Rio Mesa 6 -- Quarterback J.T. Stone's 12-yard touchdown run 
in the fourth quarter at Dos Pueblos ended hopes of a Rio Mesa comeback.Stone 
completed 18 of 33 for 301 yards, including touchdown passes of 32 and 13 
yards. 
</P>
<P>
 Dos Pueblos stopped Rio Mesa (1-4, 0-1) three times inside the Chargers' 
15-yard line. 
</P>
<P>
 Spartan running back Charlie Boch had 167 yards in four carries, including a 
73-yard touchdown run. DAVID HARRIS 
</P>
