SOUTHERN SECTION FOOTBALL ROUNDUP; NONLEAGUE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By LISA GRALL 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Moorpark 35, Kern Valley 7 -- Senior running back Bryan Wilkins rushed for 175 
yards and three touchdowns in 22 carries and caught three passes for 55 yards 
to lead host Moorpark. 
</P>
<P>
 Wilkins scored on runs of eight, six and seven yards. His eight-yard run with 
6:14 remaining in the second quarter gave Moorpark (4-0) a 21-7 lead at the 
half. 
</P>
<P>
 Cornerback Tyler Dritz recovered a bad punt snap in the end zone to hand 
Moorpark a 7-0 lead. Dritz scored in the second quarter on a 75-yard run. LISA 
GRALL 
</P>
