<TEXT>
<P>
 Balboa Bay Club -- A story Sept. 24 about a new law allowing the Balboa Bay 
Club to remain on state tidelands incorrectly stated two provisions of a 
renovation plan. The plan will open 65% of the club's facilities to the public 
and the Terrace Apartments will not be converted to a hotel, as was once 
proposed. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Correction 
</P>
</TYPE>
